Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,National Robot Museum Exhibition Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a robot called "Lightning," made with a newly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,developed glass called "pH glass."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't see anything. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't touch it, I wouldn't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,pH glass shines like a beautiful rainbow, when beamed with polarized light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream or a vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this will win the Grand Prix this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A lightning man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning Man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've waited for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to announce this year's Robot Arts Grand Prix.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The foreman of a jury, Doctor Ochanomizu, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know to what I bumped into. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me announce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This year's Robot Arts Grand Prix goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lightning Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lightning isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My money is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, how pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Banks and jewelry shops robbed; total of $10 million lost"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mystery of Ginza in the middle of the day"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Doctor, is Lightning a bad robot now, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't a bad robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the scary thing is that it's acting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,upon bad guys' orders, believing they are telling truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning doesn't know how to distinguish between good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-How are you? Did you finish vacation homework? -Yes. Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there some leads on Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Breaking news. -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,$80 million has disappeared from Shinzuku's bank safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, around 1 PM, from nine different bank safes in Shinzuku,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,cash came out and have disappeared somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the case resembles yesterday's Ginza case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the police has decided that it's done
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Skunk group using Lightning Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, Skunk? What an annoying guy. Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm going to find Skunk's hideout. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to find him in this big city? Let the police work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But rather than doing nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is Beard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That laughing sound is from Skunk. We caught him last week, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate me like other gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get out anytime if I decide to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bit sudden, but I started the work in Ginza as a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With Lightning Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? With Lightning Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a useful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it can't be seen, then it's almost like a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be calm. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you bragging about, Skunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not even responsible for today's Shinzuku case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:07:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been nothing but a liar all along. It's also a lie that you stole Lightning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't an evidence that it's done by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Who would trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Then let me show you the proof. The proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to Central Park at 6 PM. You alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise? All right? Come by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! He's trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss, are you sure you want to do that? -Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let that old beard guy make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand? Listen carefully. We are going to catch him and beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pay back within a year!" That is our motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, it's the backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-You've come well with it. -Wait, don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I found it, Skunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop it, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, I'm going to get Skunk! -You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You broke the promise, Mr. Beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. There's a reason for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses are accepted now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning, take your clothes off and finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Skunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I almost got him. What did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I did a good job, but I only made my teacher angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you are Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-I forgot about pants. -Pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I touched the legs today, it was hard. It's not like other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs? Ha ha! I'm a robot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot? I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you not know? We the robots are people's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Skunk tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know my boss' orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But what your boss is doing is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not know because you don't have much experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let me teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning, if you pick that hat for him, he would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He has no legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have worn pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Don't mess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I drink too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't wear clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take this. -Thank y...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning. Isn't it lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You shouldn't be playing around with that. It's called a Christmas tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We are having a Christmas party tomorrow night at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you shouldn't ask Skunk. Secretly come. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Would there still be good things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. The best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about telling where Skunk's hideout is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Boss will scold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tell me, please? -But I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get complimented by everyone. Please, Lighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Lightning. Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you, Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"No progress in Skunk case; the incompetence of the police"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What, is that Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-I met Lightning last night. -Wha, what? So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We became friends. So I invited him to a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He might come...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stupid! -Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you tell me that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning. It's Lightning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on. I wouldn't know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here, let's go to friends. -I have some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sprinkle those things on my clean body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, wait! -Hold on, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, if you do that, Lightning will run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can at least see his legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can figure out his destination as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That pendant has a transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With this the beard guy is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this there, Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning, where did he go? Lightning! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what is it. It's Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? Spray? -Mr. Beard sprayed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He did? Shoot. Stupid Beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Skunk's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, it doesn't work. It's not getting off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! How useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning won't be needed anymore. Now his legs can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take this timed bomb to Mr. Beard's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him "Merry Christmas."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fun sound. I want to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't want to give it to another person. -Stupid! Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It will explode at 12 AM. Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cheers! -Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop there, Skunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Lightning, Skunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He became an envoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to 12 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-12 AM? -No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu just called in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and said that Lightning showed up at Atom's place with a timed bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! What about Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion is set at 12 AM. We only have two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we still haven't found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He went to Tsukuma mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It will explode after 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The front is a national hospital with Japan's best equipments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lightning's foot prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We found the foot prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading to the worst direction possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fly to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Let's get the electronic disassemble missile ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't destroy Lightning. He's a poor one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it, if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning! Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,20 seconds remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,15 seconds remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings, but I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't blame anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to talk to Lightning for one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪ Few more nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪ Then New Year's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Year 2031, New Year's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu gave me a new year's gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. My sister Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's so mischievous that she threw the town into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran! She did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Tomboy Uran." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Tomboy Uran"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.57,0:23:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
